title: Senator Blunt Hosts Japanese Ambassador Sasae in St. Louis For Agribusiness Tour (Roy Blunt)
text: ( Source : Roy Blunt ) WASHINGTON D.C. - U.S. Senator Roy Blunt (Mo.) today hosted Japanese Ambassador Sasae for a day-long tour of facilities with an emphasis on agriculture and agribusiness including the Danforth Plant Science Center ,
